  <verse number="15" style="v" />To those who are pure, all things are pure. But to those who are stained and unbelieving, nothing is pure. For their minds and consciences have been stained. 

  <verse number="16" style="v" />They profess to know God, but they deny him by their deeds. They are detestable and disobedient. They are unapproved for any good deed.</para>
